#### Migration from Jest to `uvu`

[@&#8203;kimoofey](https://togithub.com/kimoofey) refactored all tests from the popular Jest framework to small and fast [`uvu`](https://togithub.com/lukeed/uvu).

It will not affect end-users. However, it reduced our `node_modules` size by 33 MB and made tests twice faster (`yarn install & yarn unit`: 24 â†’ 13 seconds).

